item.title: Need Help With Loading MOPARSCAPE
item.dc:creator: @hidendra Hidendra
item.description:
@hidendra wrote:

download the cache manually. http://cache.moparisthebest.com/cache.zip
extract it to : c:\windows.mpr_file_store_32 (or something similar that has mpr in it, SHOULD already be there.)
